   "speaker": "Theaetetus",
   "score": 0.0,
   "ref": "Let us assume that.",
   "new": "Very good."
  },
  {
   "ref_index": 682,
   "speaker": "Theaetetus",
   "score": 0.0515,
   "ref": "What do you say about it now?",
   "new": "And how would you amend the former statement?"
  },
  {
   "ref_index": 688,
   "speaker": "Theaetetus",
   "score": 0.0,
   "ref": "Certainly.",
   "new": "Very true."
  },
  {
   "ref_index": 698,
   "speaker": "Theaetetus",
   "score": 0.0,
   "ref": "Right.",
   "new": "True."
  },
  {
   "ref_index": 702,
   "speaker": "Theaetetus",
   "score": 0.1184,
   "ref": "I think it does, Socrates. You describe what happens to opinion marvelously well.",
   "new": "Yes, Socrates, you have described the nature of opinion with wonderful exactness."
  },
  {
   "ref_index": 706,
   "speaker": "Theaetetus",
   "score": 0.0,
   "ref": "Yes.",
   "new": "True."
  },
  {
   "ref_index": 712,
   "speaker": "Theaetetus",
   "score": 0.0,
   "ref": "Certainly.",
   "new": "Undoubtedly."
  },
  {
   "ref_index": 714,
   "speaker": "Theaetetus",
   "score": 0.0,
   "ref": "Most emphatically.",
   "new": "Entirely."
  },
  {
   "ref_index": 716,
   "speaker": "Theaetetus",
   "score": 0.0827,
   "ref": "You are right as right could be, Socrates.",
   "new": "No man, Socrates, can say anything truer than that."
  },
  {
   "ref_index": 718,
   "speaker": "Theaetetus",
   "score": 0.0,
   "ref": "Assuredly.",
   "new": "Certainly."
  },
  {
   "ref_index": 720,
   "speaker": "Theaetetus",
   "score": 0.0,
   "ref": "And true ones also.",
   "new": "Yes."
  },
  {
   "ref_index": 722,
   "speaker": "Theaetetus",
   "score": 0.0,
   "ref": "Most emphatically.",
   "new": "Undoubtedly."
  },
  {
   "ref_index": 728,
   "speaker": "Theaetetus",
   "score": 0.0696,
   "ref": "It seems to me, Socrates, that the result we have now brought out is not half bad.",
   "new": "I see no reason why we should be ashamed of our demonstration, Socrates."
  },
  {
   "ref_index": 746,
   "speaker": "Theaetetus",
   "score": 0.0481,
   "ref": "Oh yes, I remember.",
   "new": "Nay, but I am well aware."
  },
  {
   "ref_index": 760,
   "speaker": "Theaetetus",
   "score": 0.0,
   "ref": "And rightly.",
   "new": "It would be the correct expression."
  },
  {
   "ref_index": 766,
   "speaker": "Theaetetus",
   "score": 0.0486,
   "ref": "Consider it done. What next?",
   "new": "Let us imagine such an aviary--and what is to follow?"
  },
  {
   "ref_index": 768,
   "speaker": "Theaetetus",
   "score": 0.0,
   "ref": "So be it.",
   "new": "Granted."
  },
  {
   "ref_index": 770,
   "speaker": "Theaetetus",
   "score": 0.0,
   "ref": "Yes.",
   "new": "To be sure."
  },
  {
   "ref_index": 776,
   "speaker": "Theaetetus",
   "score": 0.0,
   "ref": "Certainly.",
   "new": "Exactly."
