   "score": 0.0,
   "ref": "Of course.",
   "new": "Certainly."
  },
  {
   "ref_index": 869,
   "speaker": "Theaetetus",
   "score": 0.0,
   "ref": "And very suddenly, too.",
   "new": "Yes, with wonderful celerity."
